}
```

**Nostr index.ts additions**:
```typescript
export default defineChannelPluginEntry({
  // ... standard fields ...
  registerFull(api) {
    // HTTP route registration for profile handling
    api.registerHttpRoute({
      path: "/api/channels/nostr",
      auth: "gateway",
      handler: createNostrProfileHttpHandler(/* ... */),
    });
  },
});
```

This shows how to extend plugins with HTTP APIs.

